headline: WRITER Appoints Brian O'Reilly as First Chief Operating Officer
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, February 24, 2026--WRITER, the leader in agentic AI for the enterprise, today announced the appointment of Brian O'Reilly as its first Chief Operating Officer. O’Reilly will lead the global cross-functional operations that underpin WRITER’s unified, end-to-end customer journey, from initial strategy to scaled adoption. headline: Automakers could start raising prices this year to offset tariffs, dealership executive says
summary: Tariff costs are becoming unsustainable for automakers, and they are going to have to raise prices or cut features, said the president of Sonic Automotive.
